summary: CONSUMER STATED  THERE ARE PROBLEMS WITH THE FOLLOWING:  THE FUEL INJECTION, THE FUEL LEAKS OUT OF THE FUEL FEED RAIL, AT THE SWIVEL JOINTS, THE FUEL PRESSURE REGULATOR, AND WHEN THE ENGINE COOLS DOWN THE FUEL LEAKS ALL OVER THE TOP OF THE ENGINE AND COULD CAUSE A FIRE.  THE DEALER WAS NOTIFIED AND STATED THAT THERE ISN'T A RECALL FOR THE PROBLEM.  SCC *JB
